            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Druso Caesari <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>divi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epoti</ex></expan> Divi Iuli <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>pron</abbr><ex>epoti</ex></expan> tribunicia potestate I<supplied reason="lost">I</supplied> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> II <lb n="4"/>pontufex <note>sic</note> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> Cornelius Bassus pontufex Cae<lb break="no" n="6"/>sarum <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edicavit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. Datierung: zwischen dem Beginn der 2. tribunicia potestas (März / April 23 n. Chr.) und dem Tod d. Drusus (14. 9. 23 n. Chr.); vielleicht auch postum.</p>
            </div>
